<view class="page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="eyebrow">指标解释</view>
    <view class="title">OpenRouter 与 Ramp 怎么一起看</view>
    <view class="desc">一个是推理流量前哨，一个是企业付费确认。两者不矛盾，背离本身就是信号。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="summary">
    <view class="summaryItem">
      <view class="summaryLabel">OpenRouter</view>
      <view class="summaryValue">流量领先指标</view>
    </view>
    <view class="summaryItem">
      <view class="summaryLabel">Ramp</view>
      <view class="summaryValue">付费确认指标</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:for="{{sections}}" wx:key="title" class="section">
    <view class="sectionTitle">{{item.title}}</view>
    <view class="body">{{item.body}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="sectionTitle">两套数据的口径差异</view>
    <view wx:for="{{contrasts}}" wx:key="left" class="contrastRow">
      <view class="contrastLeft">{{item.left}}</view>
      <view class="contrastRight">{{item.right}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="sectionTitle">我们的使用规则</view>
    <view wx:for="{{playbook}}" wx:key="*this" class="rule">
      <view class="dot"></view>
      <view class="ruleText">{{item}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="bottomNote">
    一句话：OpenRouter 观察“谁在拿推理流量”，Ramp 观察“谁在拿企业预算”。前者领先，后者确认。
  </view>
</view>
